{"id":230011,"date":[{"year":1951,"month":6,"day":14}],"page":"6","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"磁力","column":"","genre":"","count":"398","ytitle":"","mtitle":"安息吧，春凤姐!","ftitle":"","authors":["袁雪芬"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"袁雪芬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(编者按:钱春凤是越剧艺人筱丹桂的真名)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春凤姐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你尝遍了人世间的辛酸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"受尽了迫害与侮辱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你挣扎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你拚命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是在旧社会里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万恶的魔掌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧扼着你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你自杀了!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春凤姐吓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你可知道一现在新社会的自由天地，是多么宽广!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四周新鲜的空气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等待着你来呼吸；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是你已经与我们永别了!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春凤姐!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是谁害死了你?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是谁害死了你?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还不是那特务爪牙、恶棍流氓—"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张春帆!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他勾结了毛森那批狐群狗党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"靠山是地主；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撑腰是匪帮；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作威作福，无法无天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在越剧界称霸王!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春凤姐，安息吧!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天人民当了家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"政权在人民的手里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这恶霸特务——张春帆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再不能逃出天罗地网!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"逃不了，逃不了!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这杀人的凶手已经落了网!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春凤姐，安息吧!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的冤要报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的恨要雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你去世将近四周年了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冤沉海底的血债，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天人民政府给你讨还了!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要以敌人的血来祭奠你!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春凤姐，安息吧!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在新社会里，——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不但人民都翻了身，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连你死者的冤也都伸雪了!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春凤姐，安息吧!"}]}